To use this 2-sat solver, you must convert your problem from the following format:

(A or B) & (~A or B) & (~B or ~C)

to this format:

3 (number of clauses)

1 2
-1 2
-2 -3

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
so for every variable assign a number. To its negation, the inverse of that number.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Then run the command make run file=<filname> size=<size>

the programs will output either SAT or UNSAT
